text: I know this doesn’t add much value to the thread, but you put into words exactly how I’ve been feeling for months. It’s even more tough when it feels like no one understands. Thank you for sharing how you feel, you’ve made me feel less alone.

Does the address side of the mailer promote buying online and picking up in store? I received a notice that it was coming to my mail box on Wednesday through USPS, but my step dad threw it away. I have the code in my email and trying to figure out how long the code lasts!!
